just went off. It's beautiful.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Thousands of students from 18 countries will track Starshine  
over a six-month period, measuring the time it takes to orbit the 
Earth. By year's end it will plunge through the atmosphere and burn 
up. 
</P>
<P>
	The satellite deployment capped a busy 10-day mission.  
</P>
